This map is based on the the junkworld depicted in WALL-E. 

This map was completed very quickly, in roundabout 5 days when it should have been 5 weeks. Most of the work for this was done in the last 24 hours before the deadline so please don't judge to harshly... or do! =P

Thanks for playing, and feel free to send me any requests for changes/ports/bugfixes and i'll do whatever i can.

Cheers!
